<HTML><BODY style="word-wrap: break-word; -khtml-nbsp-mode: space; -khtml-line-break: after-white-space; "><DIV>Hi guys</DIV><DIV><BR class="khtml-block-placeholder"></DIV><DIV>I'm having problems compiling openmpi 1.2 under AIX 5.2. Here are the configure parameters:</DIV><DIV><BR class="khtml-block-placeholder"></DIV><DIV>./configure  --disable-shared --enable-static \</DIV><DIV>                   CC=xlc CXX=xlc++ F77=xlf FC=xlf95</DIV><DIV><BR class="khtml-block-placeholder"></DIV><DIV>To get it to work I have to do 2 changes:</DIV><DIV><BR class="khtml-block-placeholder"></DIV><DIV>diff -r openmpi-1.2/ompi/mpi/cxx/mpicxx.cc openmpi-1.2-aix/ompi/mpi/cxx/mpicxx.cc</DIV><DIV>34a35,38</DIV><DIV>&gt; #undef SEEK_SET</DIV><DIV>&gt; #undef SEEK_CUR</DIV><DIV>&gt; #undef SEEK_END</DIV><DIV>&gt; </DIV><DIV><BR class="khtml-block-placeholder"></DIV><DIV>diff -r openmpi-1.2/orte/mca/pls/poe/pls_poe_module.c openmpi-1.2-aix/orte/mca/pls/poe/pls_poe_module.c</DIV><DIV>636a637,641</DIV><DIV>&gt; static int pls_poe_cancel_operation(void)</DIV><DIV>&gt; {</DIV><DIV>&gt;     return ORTE_ERR_NOT_IMPLEMENTED;</DIV><DIV>&gt; }</DIV><DIV><BR class="khtml-block-placeholder"></DIV><DIV>This last one means that when you run OpenMPI jobs through POE you get a:</DIV><DIV><BR class="khtml-block-placeholder"></DIV><DIV>[r1blade003:381130] [0,0,0] ORTE_ERROR_LOG: Not implemented in file errmgr_hnp.c at line 90</DIV><DIV>--------------------------------------------------------------------------</DIV><DIV>mpirun was unable to cleanly terminate the daemons for this job. Returned value Not implemented instead of ORTE_SUCCESS.</DIV><DIV><BR class="khtml-block-placeholder"></DIV><DIV>at the job end.</DIV><DIV><BR class="khtml-block-placeholder"></DIV><DIV>Keep up the good work, cheers,</DIV><DIV><BR class="khtml-block-placeholder"></DIV><DIV>Ricardo</DIV><DIV><BR class="khtml-block-placeholder"></DIV><BR><DIV> <P style="margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px"><FONT face="Helvetica" size="3" style="font: